{"tid":628213,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到e加先發現原來有朋友等於冇朋友","createTime":"2018-04-13T15:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T09:48:45.000Z","uid":22505,"like":62,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8aeaf3c1268d0f1a3422994cf3ab7504812e9b39","tid":628213,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:26:09.000Z","msg":"平時朋友唔開心話想飲酒傾心事<br />\n我放左工就即到陪佢<br />\n但到我唔開心呢？<br />\n我話想飲酒傾心但冇一個會出黎陪我<br />\n<br />\n就而whatsapp講心事都係咁<br />\n佢地唔開心同我呻<br />\n我會企係佢地立場睇<br />\n安慰佢地﹑幫佢地分析﹑秒回<br />\n可以一傾就傾幾個鍾whatsapp<br />\n到我唔開心我whatsapp佢地掃苦<br />\n一係就hea覆埋個d<br />\n「算啦」｢唔xx都xx左喇｣｢唔好諗咁多喇｣<br />\n一係求其比個emoji我叫我收聲咁<br />\n<br />\n有朋友話想去邊<br />\n我都唔會拒絕佢地陪佢地去<br />\n就而長洲﹑大陸我都會同佢地去<br />\n到我有想去既地方﹑有想睇既戲<br />\n就會話就唔到時間﹑冇興趣睇﹑放飛機<br />\n<br />\n點解次次都係得我一個單向付出？<br />\n調反轉頭我需要佢地陪個個都拒絕我？<br />\n咁樣做朋友有咩意思？"},{"pid":"de8a495d7b8e91978508601dcf61d2a86aa2cca8","tid":628213,"uid":168960,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"香港人係咁架啦，唔信朋友呢樣野好耐"},{"pid":"565a2e4ae0e673b788aeedcf11f7e2f8f8f11630","tid":628213,"uid":93206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"起碼你有朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e1332ca7199be9937dbf28d90e99c3012a0fd2","tid":628213,"uid":22505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"565a2e4ae0e673b788aeedcf11f7e2f8f8f11630","tid":628213,"uid":93206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"起碼你有朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"只會出黎吃喝玩樂<br />\n但傾唔到心事仲有意思咩？"},{"pid":"a58c09b3ee832f402fc67088ac8390366f7aea6e","tid":628213,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e1332ca7199be9937dbf28d90e99c3012a0fd2","tid":628213,